ropean-best-destinations.jpg'),(47,'Canary Islands, Spain','The Canary Islands enjoy permanent sunshine throughout the year. For some of its islands, like Lanzarote, up to 2,500 hours of sunshine a year is reached, a record in Europe. The temperature in winter is never lower than 14 degrees (57 F) and goes up to 20 degrees (68 F) on sunny days.',111,'2021-07-01','2021-07-07','https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/none/path/sa6549607c78f5c11/image/i0c4c1ba20987caaa/version/1611753379/canary-islands-spain-best-destinations-2021.jpg'),(48,'Tübingen - Germany','This city has an incredible charm. Tübingen is definetely one of Germany\'s best hidden gems and one of the best destinations in Europe. Located just 40 minutes from Stuttgart, this city is part of the Land of Baden-Württemberg. This land is simply a must-see for castles and best hidden gems lovers in Germany.',654,'2021-07-01','2021-07-07','https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/none/path/sa6549607c78f5c11/image/i9a128cc8a5f2597c/version/1612357563/tubingen-european-best-destinations-2021-best-city-breaks-in-europe-in-2021-copyright-stephan-schlachter-european-best-destinations.jpg'),(49,'Dordogne Valley, France','With its fascinating cultural heritage and beautifully preserved natural environment, the Dordogne Valley has it all. In the summer months, the clear waters of the Dordogne river provide lots of fun activities including swimming and canoeing. It is the only river in France to be part of the UNESCO World Network of Biosphere Reserves, a prestigious recognition for an environment of exceptional quality.',223,'2021-07-01','2021-07-07','https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/none/path/sa6549607c78f5c11/image/i1b4fd472c120d338/version/1613406433/sarlat-best-destinations-in-europe-2021-copyright-editorial-shutterstock-telly-european-best-destinations.jpg'),(51,'Tahiti, French Polynesia','Located in the Pacific Ocean, The Islands of Tahiti are a mythical destination.  Surrounded by pristine, crystal clear blue waters, 118 islands and atolls offer natural beauty, authentic island culture, and unique French Polynesia style. The Islands of Tahiti are world-renowned for their white-sand beaches, stunning turquoise lagoons and varied landscapes ranging from coral atolls to volcanic mountain peaks.',555,'2021-07-01','2021-07-07','https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/none/path/sa6549607c78f5c11/image/i96ae1732a9fa8635/version/1612352393/european-best-destinations-2021-tahiti-islands-copyright-wizar.jpg'),(52,'Capri, Italy','This year discover one of the best destinations in Europe, discover Capri, its blue waters and lemon trees.',765,'2021-07-01','2021-07-07','https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/none/path/sa6549607c78f5c11/image/i86145d2102fbf1ed/version/1612801784/capri-italy-best-destinations-2021.jpg'),(53,'Braga, Portugal','The so-called Portuguese Rome is your best European destination for 2021. Braga has something to offer each of us. Braga will appeal to lovers of history and architecture. Braga is also a must-see destination for gourmets, but also for shopping addicts (with one of the largest shopping centres and a wide range of independent shops in the city centre). Braga is also a must-see destination for spirituality with sumptuous churches, monasteries and shrines.     Incredibly romantic too, Braga is one of the happiest cities in Europe and among the one with the best quality of life in the world. Still thinking about  Covid? Braga has been recognized by the OECD for the quick and innovative response of the authorities to stop the epidemic by protecting the most vulnerable.     Do you like to travel and are looking for a place to invest or settle down? Braga was voted the best destination to invest in Europe. The city is also committed to sustainable tourism and is part of the network of cities with zero CO2 emissions.',654,'2021-07-01','2021-07-07','https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/none/path/sa6549607c78f5c1